
09/Dec/2015
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Due to the "jsonevil" licensing issue reported by Lintian, the original JSON Java library
by Douglas Crockford has been replaced in JClic by the Android Team's alternative
implementation.

See:

- Original JSON Java library:

  * http://www.json.org/java/

- The "jsonevil" issue:

  * https://wiki.debian.org/qa.debian.org/jsonevil
  * https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Douglas_Crockford#.22Good.2C_not_Evil.22

- Android JSON library:

  * https://android.googlesource.com/platform/libcore/+/master/json/src/main/java/org/json


